Detailed Description

Describes a port reference in an ad-hoc connection.

PortRef a reference to a internal or external port. Internal port (spirit:internalPortReference) is a port on a component contained within the design and has a non-null componentRef. External port (spirit:externalPortReference) is a port on the component containing this design and has a null componentRef.
